/**
 * Code Quality Rules Page
 * 浠ｇ爜璐ㄩ噺瑙勫垯椤甸潰
 * 
 * Linting and code quality configuration with:
 * - Custom rule management
 * - Severity levels
 * - Rule templates
 * - Project-specific overrides
